This paper discusses the technology and prevalence of paywalls, which involves topics related to cybersecurity (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), and social implications (cs.SI). The study also involves analyzing data and building a detection mechanism, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
